# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Impossible Wordle

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

It will be a spinoff the popular daily word game, wordle. However, it will be seemingly impossible to beat.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

First it would generate a random word, accessed from dictonaries. It could use machine learning to dynamically adjust the difficulty of the feedback based on the player's previous guesses. Based on the included letters from the user's guess, it can switch around the word behind the scenes in order to increase difficulty and to make the game seemingly impossible.

