## In a paragraph or more, outline your next steps. What new skills will you need to acquire? What topics will you need to research? If working with one of two classmates, who will do what?

My next step will be to actually get started with programming. I'll need to use import random for the word selection, and I will likely use append in the code. I would need to research and explore machine learning techniques for dynamically adjusting the difficulty of the game based on the player's performance. This could involve studying natural language processing and reinforcement learning concepts. I do not plan on working with anybody, so I will be tackling this project on my owm.
